{"thag1.98:0.1":"Theragatha 1.98 ","thag1.98:0.2":"Ekakanipata ","thag1.98:0.3":"Dasamavagga ","thag1.98:0.4":"Abhayattheragatha ","thag1.98:1.1":"“Rupam disva sati muttha, ","thag1.98:1.2":"Piyam nimittam manasikaroto; ","thag1.98:1.3":"Sarattacitto vedeti, ","thag1.98:1.4":"Tanca ajjhosa titthati; ","thag1.98:1.5":"Tassa vaddhanti asava, ","thag1.98:1.6":"Bhavamulopagamino”ti. ","thag1.98:1.7":"… Abhayo thero …. "}